Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體已經送達了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我很想和克洛維斯說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快執行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}被奪走的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 為什麼會在這裡 是嫌疑犯吧  克洛維斯殿下那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說是抓錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過肯定是因為有可疑之處才會被抓的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是恐怖分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校至少會確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有區別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只是害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和他說說話就知道是怎麼樣的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行動力過於旺盛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經七年沒用過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"去屋頂說話"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事都是多虧了你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你 如果不是為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把欠你的還給你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密封艙裡的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時很混亂 我們失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你那邊 沒有她的消息嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎除了親衛隊以外誰也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於名字… 還是叫你魯魯修嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我 在記錄中已經是死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修·蘭佩魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用的是這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍事法庭那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有怎麼轉來這裡上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到魯魯修居然也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了搜查能夠順利進行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人作了這樣的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個人還說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲的話就應該好好上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是克洛維斯皇兄畫的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是皇兄呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功引出了游擊隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測其根據地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時向上匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…  柯內莉婭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊時代的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達爾頓  就是在這裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[安德列·達爾頓 Andres Darlton]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰力差距 沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧  愚蠢的ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的布里塔尼亞混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來ZERO不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐個掃蕩也真是沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就在這裡腐爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  娜娜莉  笑世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有禮物要送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然… 平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 今晚能留下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀已經是這個學校的學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以隨時都可以見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有軍隊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不是說每天都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算繼續做軍人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被調到技術部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再那麼危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好坐著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和七年前不同  今天我是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像變得穩重了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你則是變得爽快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讓你在房間待著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在新宿遇到的布里塔尼亞軍人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的話 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是… 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來  傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[吉爾伯特·G.P.·吉爾弗德 Gilbert G.P. Guilford]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於查清楚了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是排除了關於謀反的嫌疑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ORANGE君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們純血派放走了ZERO的事實卻不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官降三級
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有兩個選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼從一個初級機師重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼回鄉下去種ORANGE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在學校還是裝作不認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和名譽布里塔尼亞人是朋友什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好還會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是皇子這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你也是這樣  儘是只考慮別人的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我還會有說這句話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 你昨天好像有點奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒在學生會露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界史考試沒考好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣的說辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然新聞還沒有報導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但"武士之血"已被柯內莉婭剿滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可是中部最大的組織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在一瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說ZERO  我們再這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等待時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會聯繫你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個喜歡纏人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該和他們斷絕聯繫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[滾回…貧民區]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 吵到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒去學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 不知怎麼… 總覺得…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班裡來了個轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺害克洛維斯殿下的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙多次惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽收的是男子的名字 沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把假面藏在這裡面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Geass不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西可是能成為鐵證的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  這個香味… 又是披薩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在攢必勝客積分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有沒有變得軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[意指吃必勝客吃到虛胖哦~虛胖~]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說上臂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不准碰哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想會不會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀被人欺負了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 是需要時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想想其他辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住! 還給我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能被一隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被區區一隻貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能因為這麼白癡的事而暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有碰哦  嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼很重要的東西被貓叼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的東西是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 哥哥那種驚慌失措的慘叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修的很重要的東西究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情書?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尷尬的相片?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫情詩的小冊子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情詩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會在魯魯修之前搶回來給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他之前!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這時候那些恐怖分子在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能展開包圍作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再加深她的疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 我就這樣說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻貓怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是那個假面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忘掉  剛才看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是學生會會長米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請立即去抓住在校內逃竄的貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動全部暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協力的社團可以享受經費預算的優待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 抓住貓咪的人還將獲得超級幸運大獎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 學生會成員的吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會… 也就是說… 我的也算?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為學生會成員的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的櫻唇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會只吻下臉頰就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算臉頰也滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 可以指定位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會會員的話 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修也可以咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望是米蕾姐姐比較好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在這種情況下做百合宣言啦 (Coming-Out)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論機動力的話 我們佔絕對優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[木天蓼：貓最喜歡的"草本興奮劑",逗貓專用]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持就是勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到貓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它叼著的東西交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長… 只會多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然擅自把人當作獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說布里塔尼亞人啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害 難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初不設定成病弱少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼打扮啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是關係到我們的吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉 那隻貓有什麼特徵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它的腳可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為腳步聲稍微有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓是這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠閒的學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在明明還是服喪期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 這裡的大學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和他們談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不用把Lancelot趕出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注: NUMBERS是對被佔領地人民的通稱,比如日本為11]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說NUMBERS不行什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們學生會的人抓到它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能得到獎品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說吻的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要認真地露一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准在校內飆車!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我們的吻就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方就拜託莎莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮打算對誰用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是對… 魯魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會那樣想?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…這個嘛…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來追貓咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  學生會會長說要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了別管啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動是我的強項啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次小鳥逃掉的時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扯陳年舊事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往的體力白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經追到了是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰找到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明更加個人主義的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也過於安心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺 突然渾身脫力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托轉校生的福 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是上次那隻貓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 救了魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊 轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻貓 是不是叼著什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像戴著什麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道什麼時候就掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是有東西忘了 讓我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的『尷尬的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為終於可以抓住你的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯太愛裝帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你們兩個人是舊識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 和ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否讓他加入學生會?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校規定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生一定要加入某個社團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是副會長的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算是一事平息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都把耳朵湊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾承諾過的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就由還是半個會員的我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將就下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 為了慶祝抓住貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是由新人請客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別趁機敲詐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莎莉 多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是學生會會長米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請神聖布里塔尼亞帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第98代唯一皇帝陛下發言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 是不平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生來就健行之人  美貌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母貧困之人  病弱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生  成長  才能  所有人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是為了被差別對待而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人類才會爭鬥  競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此才產生了進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不平等並非惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等才有惡處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高呼權利平等的EU怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[EU：Europe Union，假想的歐洲同盟]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任期只是導致了眾愚政治而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[任期制：同帝國繼承製相反]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求平等均富的中華聯邦呢?  造就了一群懈怠的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我們布里塔尼亞並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭鬥  競爭  一直持續著在進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化? 真是個好詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有布里塔尼亞在前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未來在前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾子克洛維斯之死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是布里塔尼亞在持續進化的最佳證明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競爭  掠奪  獲取  支配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此盡頭  有著未來!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:22:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修的敵人…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"否定"這個詞都顯得太溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個男人就是布里塔尼亞的象徵的話 我就摧毀他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在這條路上 還有皇姐柯內莉婭阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經擁有了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隻身一人也能…
